<div class="container theme-showcase" role="main">
  <div class="bs-callout bs-callout-info">
    <p class="lead">Hello <code><%= @userfullname.split.map(&:capitalize).join(' ') %></code>. Welcome to Cloudwick's SYNC Portal.</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Sync is a centralized portal for making requests for documents, certifications, air tickets, servers; view training content; Fill timesheets; update your projects and related information.</h3>

  <br>

  <h3>Other tools:</h3>

  <div class="col-xs-3 spacer">
    <div class="well" style="height:250px; background-color: #337ab7;">
      <p align="center" class="font-responsive-large"><a href="https://cloudwick.atlassian.net/wiki"><font color="white">Cloudwick Athenaeum</font></a></p>
      <br>
      <p align="center"><font color="white">Centralized knowledge management. You will be able to sign in using your cloudwick email address.</font></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-3 spacer">
    <div class="well" style="height:250px; background-color: #5bc0de;">
      <p align="center" class="font-responsive-large"><a href="https://cloudwick.atlassian.net/wiki/questions"><font color="white">Cloudwick Questions</font></a></p>
      <br>
      <p align="center"><font color="white">If you have any technical questions this is the place to ask. You will be able to sign in using your cloudwick email address.</font></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-3 spacer">
    <div class="well" style="height:250px; background-color: #5cb85c;">
      <p align="center" class="font-responsive-large"><a href="https://cloudwick.hipchat.com"><font color="white">HipChat</font></a></p>
      <br>
      <p align="center"><font color="white">Team colloboration and chat. To sign up to hipchat use this <a href="https://cloudwick.hipchat.com/invite/132959/a3b976f705b0c09ecf462f9ce7d3ba02">link</a> and use your cloudwick email address when signing up.</font></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-3 spacer">
    <div class="well" style="height:250px; background-color: #f0ad4e;">
      <p align="center" class="font-responsive-large"><a href="https://github.com/cloudwicklabs"><font color="white">Cloudwick Github</font></a></p>
      <br>
      <p align="center"><font color="white">Code sharing.</font></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <br>

  <p><code>Feedback</code>: We will be happy to hear back from you on how to better build this platform. Contact Sync <a href="mailto:syncadmin@cloudwick.com?subject:Suggestion about Sync from <%= @userfullname %>">admin(s)</a> for more information or to send suggestions.</p>
</div>

